title: "Dormer Three"- A Fully Furnished Apt in Uptown
posting_body: ['$1100 - Monthly rate', '$285 plus $45 cleaning - Weekly rate', '$45 plus $45 cleaning - Daily rate', 'This charming apartment features herringbone tiling, rich dark wood paneled wall, trendy barn wood accent and decadently luxurious in-floor heating.', 'You will enjoy many modern amenities and conveniences in a house where the splendor of the Victorian era has been lovingly preserved.', "You'll enter this unique space through the main entrance, pass through a hallway and enter your private room.", 'Inside, the brand new queen size bed features a cozy quilt plus 500 thread count sheets.', 'This room also features desk nook for your office needs.', 'The closet is equipped with an iron and ironing board.', 'Guests also have access to the washer and dryer and and free on-street parking.', 'This room offers access to a shared bathroom and kitchen.', 'The automatic Keurig coffee and tea maker along with pods starts your mornings with ease.', 'The fully equipped kitchen includes a gas stove, microwave oven and fridge.', 'Meal prep is simple with a full set of cookware, knives and spices.', 'Enjoy your meal on china dishes at the high top table.', 'The newly remodeled bathroom features all new black tile and twin sinks.', 'You’ll find the shower well stocked with shampoo, conditioner, body wash, a fresh bar of soap and fluffy white towels in your room.', 'My 1895 era house is located in Uptown, one of the most walkable neighborhoods in Minneapolis.', 'You’ll find yourself a short walk from the Walker Art Museum and its famous “Spoon Bridge” sculpture, Lake of the Isles, Spyhouse Coffee, The Wedge Coop Grocery Store, and The Basilica of St. Mary.', 'Contact Daniel at', 'show contact info', '$1100 per month', 'I will provide you with a key upon arrival.', 'You are renting one of six units in my home.', 'Interaction with guests', 'I am as available as you need me to be.', "Don't hesitate to call or text with questions, even if you just need a restaurant suggestion.", "I'm here!", 'My name is Daniel.', 'I purchased this house in 2001 and have been lovingly renovating it ever since.', 'I have honored the spirit of the original building while thoughtfully adding my own touches and inspiration.', 'One of my great passions in life is Argentine Tango, so I named each apartment after a beloved Argentine musician.', 'If you are curious about the dance scene in the Twin Cities, I’m happy to point you towards the best milongas and I also offer lessons.']
